pupils they decided to investigate a claim by a tea bag maufacturer that his 
new tetrahedral tea bags gave the tea twice as much space to brew.  In a 
simple minded way she got them to work out  the volume of a tetrahedron
and then turned to the "easy" case of the square bags....disaster.

