&gt;following was brought to notice by David Eppstein
&gt;
&gt;&lt;<A HREF="http://www.ics.uci.edu/~eppstein/junkyard/teabag.html">http://www.ics.uci.edu/~eppstein/junkyard/teabag.html</A>&gt;<A HREF="http://www.ics.uci.edu/~eppstein/junkyard/teabag.html">http://www.ics.uci.edu/~eppstein/junkyard/teabag.html</A>
